785
01:05:15,800 --> 01:05:18,439
Sweetheart, it's okay. No harm, no--

786
01:05:20,320 --> 01:05:22,993
I'm so sorry again, Rick.

787
01:05:23,800 --> 01:05:24,949
You spoiled bitch.

788
01:05:27,000 --> 01:05:28,149
Be cool.

789
01:05:29,480 --> 01:05:31,118
Come on!

790
01:05:34,720 --> 01:05:35,835
Pussy.

791
01:05:40,800 --> 01:05:44,998
It says Zyprexa is used to treat the
symptoms of psychotic conditions...

792
01:05:45,160 --> 01:05:48,516
...such as schizophrenia
and bipolar disorder.

793
01:05:48,680 --> 01:05:51,035
I just thought she was weird.

794
01:05:52,200 --> 01:05:55,988
Maybe this is a refill. Maybe she's
been taking them the whole time.

795
01:05:56,160 --> 01:05:58,469
Yeah, I don't think
she's ever taken them.

796
01:06:00,160 --> 01:06:02,355
I think it's time
to move in with Irene.

797
01:06:02,680 --> 01:06:04,113
Yeah.

798
01:06:42,880 --> 01:06:45,155
